name: Akabeko
description: Bali, Japan and omamori (charm/amulet) are among my favorite things. Akabeko is a legendary cow that is believed to be able to ward off illnesses. In Indonesia, farmer's boy usually rides on a cow while tending on their rice fields. So i combined both in a drawing, with a hope that we can go through this year safely and in good health. This will be a personal memento for me too, of these weird 2020-2021 :)
